> Yes, you should. On an ADC it is a great item. Both defenses make you more resistant to magic damage yes, but also physical damage which is minions, turrets, basic attacks, objectives, jungle camps, ADCs, AD assassins, AD bruisers, AD tanks. Having that hybrid defense alone is worth it. The auto resurrection is just an amazing 5 minute CD. Unless they have more CC and less burst, then you should get {{item:3139}}

if your build is {{item:3087}} {{item:3031}} {{item:3006}} {{item:3036}} {{item:3026}}

Then your 6th item wont let you reach over 50% crit rate or have any lifesteal.

Thats why GA is generally bad.
